				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I've been hearing such nice things about Headshot, and being so poor, I decided to go for it!   I got my HS and headed to AC to farm some acrylia.  
<br />

<br />
Here's my question:   I shoot dozens of arrows at a mob and either get no HS, or it goes off when the mob is down to like 20% health.   I keep reading about HS going off on the first few arrows per mob.   What am I doing wrong?   I have EQ/AM3 and a Stonewood Compound bow.
<br />

<br />
Any help would be greatly appreciated!
<br />

<br />
Erinanne</span><span class="gentblsmall"></span></td>
