				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">It's purely random . . .
<br />

<br />
BUT, it's widely documented that the Random Number Generator is very streaky. Next time you go, you may headshot three in a row on the first arrow you shoot at them.
<br />

<br />
I think the RNG has a personality and hates us because we share it's abbreviation <img src="images/smiles/icon_smile.gif" alt="icon_smile.gif" border="0" /><br />_________________<br />Baron Aquendar Lerilon
