				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Since we are in conjecture land, I will make two observations:
<br />

<br />
Headshot seems to have a greatly increased frequency of triggering when fired at a mobile target that has not yet aggroed (i.e. first shot). This could be related to the side/back thing mentioned above.
<br />

<br />
Headshot seems to have a greatly increased frequency of triggering when there is more than one target aggroed in an area. I have no theories on this one.
<br />

<br />
